      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَمَّنْ بَاتَ لَيَالِيَ مِنًى بِمَكَّةَ فَقَالَ «عَلَيْهِ ثَلاَثَةٌ مِنَ اَلْغَنَمِ يَذْبَحُهُنَّ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3007 - Ibn Maskan narrated from Ja’far ibn Najiyah, from Abu Abdullah (as):\nI asked him about someone who spends the nights of Mina in Mecca.\nImam (as) replied: \"He must offer three sheep as a sacrifice.\""
